{"id":2021,"date":"2021-03-24T11:28:42","date_gmt":"2021-03-24T11:28:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/?p=2021"},"modified":"2021-10-07T10:39:51","modified_gmt":"2021-10-07T10:39:51","slug":"nguon-goc-saffron","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/nguon-goc-saffron\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y &#038; l\u1ee3i \u00edch th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 Saffron"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y hay saffron l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn cho con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng b\u00ed m\u1eadt v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb. V\u1eady <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/nguon-goc-saffron\/\"><b>ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u? L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a saffron nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eadt m\u00ed ngay qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y\u00a0<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e2y ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y sinh tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u1ea5t \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c v\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ecba Trung H\u1ea3i. Kh\u00ed h\u1eadu t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00f4 h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lu\u1ed3ng gi\u00f3 n\u00f3ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 m\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 trung b\u00ecnh kho\u1ea3ng -10 \u0111\u1ed9 C th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb tuy\u1ebft bao ph\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u1eadu n\u00e0y thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e2y ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 cho ra \u0111\u1eddi nh\u1eefng s\u1ee3i saffron ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2023\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2023\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2023 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-nguon-goc.jpg\" alt=\"Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nhu\u1ef5 hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-nguon-goc.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-nguon-goc-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-nguon-goc-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2023\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nhu\u1ef5 hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 qu\u1ed1c gia tr\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2y ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0: Iran, Hy L\u1ea1p, \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, T\u00e2y Ban Nha,&#8230; v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Saffron c\u1ee7a Iran\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u00e0 th\u1ed5 nh\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u1ea1i Iran c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 sinh tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u00e2y ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &#8220;th\u1ee7 ph\u1ee7 &#8221; c\u1ee7a nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y. L\u01b0\u1ee3ng saffron s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Iran chi\u1ebfm 90-93% t\u1ed5ng s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> t\u1eeb Iran th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1i cao c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng tr\u1ed3ng kh\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u00f9ng canh t\u00e1c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t saffron ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu t\u1ea1i Iran c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Badiee, Goliran, Bahraman.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron Iran c\u00f3 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1edbt cao, h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01a1m thanh m\u00e1t, d\u1ecbu ng\u1ecdt c\u00f3 l\u1eabn m\u00f9i c\u1ecf c\u00e2y \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng. T\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, saffron Iran chi\u1ebfm ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Hy L\u1ea1p<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2024\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2024\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2024 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-hy-lap.jpg\" alt=\"Hy L\u1ea1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng qu\u1ed1c gia xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 nh\u1ee5y hoa n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 sau Iran\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-hy-lap.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-hy-lap-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-hy-lap-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2024\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hy L\u1ea1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng qu\u1ed1c gia xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 nh\u1ee5y hoa n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 sau Iran<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Hy L\u1ea1p. Gi\u1ed1ng c\u00e2y ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ed3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c ng\u00e0n n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau n\u00e0y, th\u00f4ng qua giao th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e2n r\u1ed9ng ra c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e2n c\u1eadn. Theo t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng saffron xu\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9u ra b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau Iran.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 trong xu\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9u s\u1ee3i nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y. T\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, c\u00e2y ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u1edf v\u00f9ng Kashmir. S\u1ee3i saffron t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u00e2n d\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ea7u d\u00e0y h\u01a1n v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eabm (c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i saffron kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf cam). Saffron \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u00f9i th\u1ea3o m\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i saffron n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Saffron c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb Maroc<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maroc ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia ti\u1ebfp theo c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y l\u1edbn tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c, nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u1edf Maroc \u00edt b\u00e1n l\u1ebb v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t theo \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e2y kh\u00e1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nhu\u1ef5 hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2025\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2025\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2025 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u00a0\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tay-ban-nha.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tay-ban-nha-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tay-ban-nha-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2025\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u00a0<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ed3ng \u1edf th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Madrid. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ra \u0111\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u saffron n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Princesa de Minaya. <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/thanh-phan-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay\/\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea9m saffron<\/a> t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n theo b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gia truy\u1ec1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi qu\u00fd t\u1ed9c T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Do \u0111\u00f3 h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean, saffron c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ed3ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 qu\u1ed1c gia Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 \u00edt. B\u1edfi gi\u00e1 c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n cao, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a Saffron Iran n\u00ean saffron c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5t s\u1ed1ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia nh\u01b0 \u00c1o, Anh, \u0110\u1ee9c, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, Ph\u00e1p, Israel, Mexico, Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 t\u1ef1 tr\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 thu ho\u1ea1ch saffron ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ecf.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a saffron\u00a0<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi v\u00ec ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2028\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2028\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2028 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-ngu-ngon.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng an th\u1ea7n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon v\u00e0 s\u00e2u h\u01a1n\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-ngu-ngon.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-ngu-ngon-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-ngu-ngon-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2028\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng an th\u1ea7n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon v\u00e0 s\u00e2u h\u01a1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng an th\u1ea7n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi hay ch\u1ecbu \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c. Nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y nh\u01b0 Crocin v\u00e0 safanal s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam, ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng gi\u00fap ng\u1ee7 ngon v\u00e0 s\u00e2u h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"pLQuuBiNge\"><p><a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/saffron-tri-mat-ngu\/\">C\u00e1ch U\u1ed1ng Saffron Nh\u1ee5y Hoa Ngh\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Tr\u1ecb M\u1ea5t Ng\u1ee7\u00a0<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;C\u00e1ch U\u1ed1ng Saffron Nh\u1ee5y Hoa Ngh\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Tr\u1ecb M\u1ea5t Ng\u1ee7\u00a0&#8221; &#8212; Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/saffron-tri-mat-ngu\/embed\/#?secret=pLQuuBiNge\" data-secret=\"pLQuuBiNge\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<h3><b>\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ee9ng tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/saffron\/\">saffron<\/a> c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m. C\u00e1c h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5t trong s\u1ee3i nh\u1ee5y hoa s\u1ebd gi\u00fap th\u1ea7n kinh n\u00e3o \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kho\u1ea3ng 10-15 s\u1ee3i nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian li\u00ean t\u1ee5c 6 tu\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 th\u1ea7n kinh kh\u00e1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Gi\u1ea3m tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng ti\u1ec1n kinh nguy\u1ec7t\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2027\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2027\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2027 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-phu-nu-tien-man-kinh.jpg\" alt=\"Saffron gi\u00fap l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng ti\u1ec1n m\u00e3n kinh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-phu-nu-tien-man-kinh.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-phu-nu-tien-man-kinh-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-phu-nu-tien-man-kinh-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2027\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Saffron gi\u00fap l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng ti\u1ec1n m\u00e3n kinh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng gi\u1ea3m c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng ti\u1ec1n kinh nguy\u1ec7t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9ng b\u1ec7nh nh\u01b0 \u0111au b\u1ee5ng, \u0111au l\u01b0ng, c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n kinh nguy\u1ec7t s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>T\u1ed1t cho h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a saffron. C\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y gi\u00fap l\u00e0m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh huy\u1ebft \u00e1p \u1edf ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed huy\u1ebft \u00e1p cao. C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, saffron kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng hay c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba ung th\u01b0\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo c\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u khoa h\u1ecdc, nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u00e2y b\u1ec7nh. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n x\u1ea5u. Ch\u1ea5t crocin trong saffron ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh ung th\u01b0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u1ea5u \u0103n ho\u1eb7c pha tr\u00e0.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a saffron kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1eaft v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c. Lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eaft c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng m\u1eaft, tho\u00e1i h\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0ng, gi\u00e1c m\u1ea1c,&#8230; \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong saffron c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u vitamin A gi\u00fap m\u1eaft lu\u00f4n s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p\u00a0<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2026\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2026\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2026 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-lam-dep.jpg\" alt=\"T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-lam-dep.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-lam-dep-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-lam-dep-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2026\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m s\u1eb9o, m\u1ee5n: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng saffron th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e1nh bay c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n, tr\u1ecb th\u00e2m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. \u0110em l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m, n\u00e1m: C\u00e1c vitamin, protein c\u00f3 trong Saffron th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ea3n sinh ra collagen v\u00e0 elastin. Gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c v\u1ebft th\u00e2m n\u00e1m hay xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n s\u1edbm, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i: C\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong saffron cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m gi\u00fap da kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o da lu\u00f4n c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn, tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y, <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/\">Lifenest Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/a> \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nhu\u1ef5 hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Hy v\u1ecdng, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ed5 \u00edch tr\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n an t\u00e2m h\u01a1n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u00e0y!\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y hay saffron l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn cho con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng b\u00ed m\u1eadt v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb. V\u1eady ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nh\u1ee5y [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2029,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_seopress_robots_primary_cat":"none"},"categories":[20],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2021"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2021"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2021\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3958,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2021\/revisions\/3958"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2029"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2021"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2021"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2021"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}